'''熊田偶联反应'''（{{lang|ja|熊田カップリング}}，{{lang|en|Kumada coupling}}），又称'''熊田-玉尾-Corriu偶联反应'''（{{lang|ja|熊田・玉尾・コリューカップリング}}，{{lang|en|Kumada-Tamao-Corriu coupling}}），指[[烷基|烷基]]或[[芳基|芳基]][[格氏试剂|格氏试剂]]与芳[[卤代烃|卤]]或[[乙烯基|乙烯基]]卤在[[镍|镍]]或[[钯|钯]]催化下的[[交叉偶联反应|交叉偶联反应]]。反应产物为[[苯乙烯|苯乙烯]]衍生物。

此反应在1972年由[[熊田誠|熊田誠]]（{{jpn|j=熊田 誠|hg=くまだ まこと|rm=Kumada Makoto}}）与 Robert J. P. Corriu 分别同时报道。类似的反应还有[[铃木反应|铃木反应]]、[[薗头偶合反应|薗头偶合反应]]等。

==历史==
计量格氏试剂发生的自偶联反应很早就已知道。 关于格氏试剂与卤代烃之间偶联反应的研究最早是在1971年，当时 Tamura 和 Kochi 发展了用银<ref>{{cite journal en| title = Mechanism of the silver-catalyzed reaction of Grignard reagents with alkyl halides | author = Jay K. Kochi and Masuhiko Tamura | journal = [[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]] | year = 1971 | volume = 93 | issue = 6 | pages = 1483–1485 | doi = 10.1021/ja00735a028}}</ref>、铜<ref>''Alkylcopper(I) in the coupling of Grignard reagents with alkyl halides'' Jay K. Kochi, Masuhiko Tamura [[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]], 1971, 93 (6), pp 1485–1487 {{DOI|10.1021/ja00735a029}}</ref>、和铁<ref>''Vinylation of Grignard reagents. Catalysis by iron'' Masuhiko Tamura, Jay K. Kochi [[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]], 1971, 93 (6), pp 1487–1489 {{DOI|10.1021/ja00735a030}}</ref> 催化剂催化的交叉偶联反应。

1972年，[[熊田誠|熊田誠]]（{{jpn|j=熊田 誠|hg=くまだ まこと|rm=Kumada Makoto}}）等<ref>{{cite journal en| title = Selective carbon-carbon bond formation by cross-coupling of Grignard reagents with organic halides. Catalysis by nickel-phosphine complexes | author = Kohei Tamao, Koji Sumitani, Makoto Kumada | journal = [[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]] | year = 1972 | volume = 94 | issue = 12 | pages = 4374–4376 | doi = 10.1021/ja00767a075}}</ref> 报道了格氏试剂（[[苯基溴化镁|苯基溴化镁]]）与芳卤或乙烯基卤在镍催化剂 NiCl<sub>2</sub>(dppe)<sub>2</sub> 作用之下交叉偶联为[[苯乙烯|苯乙烯]]的反应。


:[[Image:KumadaReactionI.png|500px]]

同年，Robert J. P. Corriu等<ref>{{cite journal en| title = Activation of Grignard Reagents by Transition-metal Complexes. A New and Simple Synthesis of trans-Stilbenes and Polyphenyls | author = Corriu, R. J. P.; Masse, J. P. | journal = [[J._Chem._Soc.,_Chem._Commun.|J. Chem. Soc., Chem. Commun.]] | year = 1972 | pages = 144 | doi = 10.1039/c3972000144a}}</ref> 发现苯基溴化镁与β-溴苯乙烯在[[乙醚|乙醚]]溶剂中和另一镍催化剂——[[乙酰丙酮合镍(II)|乙酰丙酮合镍(II)]]催化之下，可得反-[[二苯乙烯|二苯乙烯]]。


:[[Image:KumadaCoupling_Corriu_1973.svg|Corriu 1972]]

此后，1975年[[村橋俊一|村橋俊一]]（{{jpn|j=村橋 俊一|hg=むらはし しゅんいち|rm=Murahashi Shun-ichi}}）等<ref>{{cite journal en| title = The reaction of σ-vinylpalladium complexes with alkyllithiums. Stereospecific syntheses of olefins from vinyl halides and alkyllithiums | journal = [[J._Organomet._Chem.|J. Organomet. Chem.]] | volume = 91 | issue = 2 | year = 1975 | pages = C39–C42 | author = Masaaki Yamamura, Ichiro Moritani and Shun-Ichi Murahashi | doi = 10.1016/S0022-328X(00)89636-9}}</ref> 将此反应拓展至钯催化。

==反应机理==
[[File:Katalysezyklus-Kumada-Kupplung.png|center]]

从右上顺时针旋转依次为：[[氧化加成|氧化加成]]、[[转金属|转金属]]、[[顺反异构化|顺反异构化]]、[[还原消除|还原消除]]。

==拓展==
此反应亦被拓展至芳基格氏试剂（由芳碘与异丙基氯化镁／[[氯化锂|氯化锂]]原位制备<ref>{{cite journal | title = A LiCl-Mediated Br/Mg Exchange Reaction for the Preparation of Functionalized Aryl- and Heteroarylmagnesium Compounds from Organic Bromides  | author = Arkady Krasovskiy, [[Paul_Knochel|Paul Knochel]] | journal = [[Angewandte_Chemie_International_Edition|Angewandte Chemie International Edition]] | volume = 43 | issue = 25 | pages = 3333–3336 | year = 2004 | doi = 10.1002/anie.200454084}}</ref>）与芳卤之间的偶联，生成联芳烃，而且反应对官能团有更强的耐受性。<ref>{{cite journal en| title = Pd-Catalyzed Kumada-Corriu Cross-Coupling Reactions at Low Temperatures Allow the Use of Knochel-type Grignard Reagents | author = Ruben Martin and Stephen L. Buchwald | journal = [[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]] | year = 2007 | volume = 129 | issue = 13 | pages = 3844–3845 | format = Communication | doi = 10.1021/ja070830d}}</ref>

